### 1. Create account - success
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "192456789",
  "customerName": "Joe Wu",
  "accountNickName": "New Zealand",
  "accountType": "01",
  "channelCode": "01",
  "branchCode": "0278",
  "currency": "NZD",
  "transactionReference": "TXN-3097"
}

